The paper discusses distributed algorithms for expected loss minimization, which is a common problem in machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with distributed computing, which suggests categories such as cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms). The use of iterative methods and optimization techniques suggests categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NA (Numerical Analysis).
